            </article>
            <article class="blurb third">
                <h4><%- gettext('Password-free for 700 million') %></h4>
                <p><%- gettext('Persona allows users to sign into sites with any email address, but is especially convenient for Gmail & Yahoo addresses where no new password need be created.') %></p>
            </article>
        </section>

